A "listener journey" validator \'97 not just "are these books different enough?" but "does the series make sense as a reading order?" Adjacent installments shouldn't just avoid repetition; they should create momentum\
\ls6\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	4	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
