Build compatible candidates for each knob (filtered by topic compatibility, duration compatibility)\cb1 \
\ls47\ilvl0\cb7 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	3	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Score each candidate combination:\cb1 \
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\partightenfactor0
\ls47\ilvl1\cf2 \cb7 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Compatibility score (topic \'d7 knob fit)\cb1 \
\ls47\ilvl1\cb7 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Narrative quality score (journey_shape \'d7 chapter_archetype coherence)\cb1 \
\ls47\ilvl1\cb7 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Anti-cluster penalty from wave index (penalize combos used in recent waves)\cb1 \
\ls47\ilvl1\cb7 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Series diversity penalty (penalize combos used by other installments in same series)\cb1 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls47\ilvl0\cf2 \cb7 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	4	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Apply hard caps: No combo may exceed 15% of total catalog. No knob value may exceed 30% of wave.\cb1 \
\ls47\ilvl0\cb7 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	5	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Deterministic selection: Top-scoring combination wins. Stable tie-break by seed.\cb1 \
\ls47\ilvl0\cb7 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	6	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Persist: Write variation_signature + all knob values to plan output and similarity index.\cb1 \
