\cb7 Narration Assignment Rules\cb1 \
\cb7 AI narration willingness among US listeners dropped from 77% (2023) to 70% (2025), even as AI-narrated consumption increased. This means AI narration is a conversion risk for high-value titles where voice trust drives purchase.\cb1 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs24 \cf5 \cb14 yaml\cb1 \
