\f1 \uc0\u8594 
\f0  follow 
\f1 \uc0\u8594 
\f0  stream 
\f1 \uc0\u8594 
\f0  complete 
\f1 \uc0\u8594 
\f0  next title.\
\
  \cf17 hours_cap_strategy\cf18 :\cf21 \
    \cf18 -\cf21  \cf17 premium_hours\cf18 :\cf21  "~15 hours/month included"\
    \cf18 -\cf21  \cf17 audiobooks_plus\cf18 :\cf21  "Top-up hours available via Audiobooks+"\
    \cf18 -\cf21  \cf17 implication\cf18 :\cf21  \cf18 >\cf21 \
        Shorter titles (1-3h) get more plays per subscriber per month.\
