\fs32 \cf2 \cb7 Layer 1: Flagship Titles (68)\cb1 \
\cb7 From the production grid, 68 persona \'d7 topic combinations marked "F."\
Each gets: human narration, unique title+subtitle, active marketing, ACX exclusive.\cb1 \
\cb7 Layer 2: Persona Variants (52)\cb1 \
\cb7 52 combinations marked "V."\
Each gets: AI narration, persona subtitle, $9.95, wide distribution.\cb1 \
\cb7 Layer 3: Short-Form (6)\cb1 \
\cb7 6 combinations marked "S" (Gen Alpha).\
Each gets: AI narration, 1-2 hours, $4.99-$7.99, Spotify.\cb1 \
\cb7 Layer 4: Engine Angle Variants (\'d72-3 per flagship, \'d72 per variant)\cb1 \
