\fs32 \cf2 \cb7 Layer 5: Model B Depth Variants (Tier 1 Topics Only)\cb1 \
\cb7 5 Tier 1 topics \'d7 6 primary personas \'d7 2 depth levels = 60 titles. Subtract the originals (already counted): 60 - 30 = 30 additional depth books.\cb1 \
\cb7 Layer 6: Location Variants (Gen Z + Gen Alpha)\cb1 \
\cb7 Gen Z has 23 location variable files. Gen Alpha has 25.\
Top 5 topics \'d7 23 Gen Z locations = 115 location variants.\
Top 4 topics \'d7 10 Gen Alpha locations = 40 location variants.\cb1 \
\cb7 Many of these are variable-only (no new templates needed): 155 location variant titles.\cb1 \
\cb7 Layer 7: Seasonal and Trending\cb1 \
\cb7 Tax anxiety (March-April), holiday stress (Nov-Dec), back-to-school (September), New Year reset (January). Special-angle titles timed to search spikes.\cb1 \
\cb7 ~50 seasonal titles across the year.\cb1 \
\cb7 Layer 8: Bundles and Compilations\cb1 \
\cb7 3-book topic bundles: 12 topics \'d7 3 primary personas = 36 bundles. "Complete Library" persona bundles: 10 personas \'d7 1 = 10 bundles.\cb1 \
\cb7 Layer 9: Companion Audio Exercises / Freebies\cb1 \
\cb7 Short-form (15-30 min) guided practices. Not full books but catalog entries. 12 topics \'d7 3 primary exercise types \'d7 3 personas = ~108 audio exercises.\cb1 \
