\fs36 \cf2 \cb7 14. Summary\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs32 \cf2 \cb7 The catalog is 1,008 standalone books organized into overlapping series. Each book owns a search term, targets a specific persona, and delivers a complete therapeutic journey. No book depends on any other book.\cb1 \
\cb7 Three models layer to maximize variety while minimizing writing:\cb1 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls49\ilvl0\cf2 \cb7 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Model A (topic) provides the spine \'97 12 topics with distinct engines\cb1 \
\ls49\ilvl0\cb7 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Model C (persona) provides the multiplier \'97 10 personas with distinct voices\cb1 \
\ls49\ilvl0\cb7 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Model B (depth) provides the curriculum \'97 Tier 1 topics get Foundations + Advanced\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \cb7 Seven variation knobs ensure structural uniqueness: book_structure_id, journey_shape_id, chapter_archetypes, section_reorder_mode, motif_id, reframe_profile_id 
\f1 \uc0\u8594 
\f0  variation_signature\cb1 \
\cb7 Five enforcement levels prevent repetition: within-book, within-series, within-wave, catalog-wide, market-level\cb1 \
\cb7 Title = search keyword. Subtitle = persona hook. Generated from templates. Every book gets a unique, market-ready title+subtitle combination.\cb1 \
\cb7 The first 30 seconds of every book is a conversion surface. Problem statement 
\f1 \uc0\u8594 
\f0  tool preview 
\f1 \uc0\u8594 
\f0  tone trust cue, engineered for Spotify's preview-to-stream funnel. This is the highest-leverage production spec in the system.\cb1 \
\cb7 Narration follows revenue logic. Human narration for Tier 1 flagships and high-trust topics (somatic, sleep, grief). AI narration for variants, short-form, and Gen Alpha. AI narration willingness is declining \'97 treat voice trust as a conversion variable, not just a cost variable.\cb1 \
\cb7 Platform rules are system rules. Google Play promo mechanics (scheduled discounts, promo codes, series bundles) and Spotify discovery signals (search/listen/skip/save 
\f1 \uc0\u8594 
\f0  taste profile) are built into the distribution config, not left to marketing. Release scheduling, file naming, and preorder pipeline are automated across 24 brands.\cb1 \
\cb7 Compliance is a lint layer, not a disclaimer. FTC health claims rules, platform content policies, and therapeutic guardrails (polyvagal framing, habit formation timelines, depression safety) are enforced at the content generation level through banned phrases, required disclaimers, and safe positioning language. "Not medical advice" disclaimers do not fix implied cure claims \'97 the content itself must be clean.\cb1 \
\cb7 Revenue-tiered personas drive production priority: Build for millennial women, tech/finance, and entrepreneurs first (60% of addressable revenue). Existing Gen Z and healthcare atoms provide Tier 3 catalog depth immediately.\cb1 \
\cb7 The catalog grows multiplicatively while writing effort grows additively. Mechanisms are authored once. Engines once per topic. Templates once per persona. Variables once per persona \'d7 location. Atoms are the main writing \'97 constrained by everything above to ~60% less effort per atom than free-writing.\cb1 \
}